                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">霜見雪關扉</span>。</p>",
