                "title": "神里流·霜滅"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】此角色被切換爲「出戰角色」時，附屬<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素附魔</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/08/84496276/7359eeec791acae26196aa72a0621268_985306290348843906.png",
                "id": "talent72386",
                "key": "神里流·霰步",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神里流·霰步"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">造成2點</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/21/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7199018360585379110.png",
                "id": "talent16631",
                "key": "霜見雪關扉",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/21/84496276/1447ebe24c4e7bd955c4b795be517cd3_9881600191564857.png",
                "title": "霜見雪關扉"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/21/84496276/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_5267871960264012096.png",
                "id": "talent88422",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冰元素附魔</span></strong></p><p>所附屬角色的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>。</p><p>（持續到回合結束）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/21/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_486441729685358826.png",
